# the code is only tested with raspian - debian for  raspberrry pi

# In order to run the script
  - copy files into  /usr/local/bin
  - copy wenv.default.sh into wenv.sh
       - cp wenv.default.sh wenv.sh
  - Update the parms to reflect your site environment
  - scripts provided 
      - wnet_ping.sh 192.168.1.2   for connectivity testing
  
      - wnet_scan.sh for network scan
